# Cursor Ignore - Files to ignore in suggestions

# Documentation files (unless explicitly requested)
*.md
!README.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!tmp/*.md

# Temporary files and directories
# tmp/ folder hosts auxiliary scripts and markdown files - these should be accessible
tmp/*
!tmp/.gitkeep
!tmp/README.md
!tmp/*.md
!tmp/*.py
!tmp/*.sh
!tmp/*.json
!tmp/*.csv

# Other temporary file patterns
*.tmp
*_temp.*
*_test_temp.*

# But allow if explicitly in path when user requests
# This prevents automatic creation but allows explicit requests
